fields.content:
The landing page for the site.  It is by far the most intricate and customizable part of the site. I have filled it with some default values already but this website is your oyster.

Here's your guide:

Slider:

Slider images should be 1920x690.

I personally find lowering the birghtness makes the images look better.

I see this being used to give shoutouts to sponsors.

Featured companies:

Perhaps a place to give shoutouts to companies that didn't sponsor us but we like anyway, idk.

Images should be squares.  It doesn't matter what size as long as it's a perfect square.

Announcements:

A blurb of text, an author, and a body.  You can't mess this up
fields.heading: 38th Annual NSBE/SHPE Career Fair
fields.subheading: Located in Troy, NY, the NSBE/SHPE Career Fair has successfully hosted over 200 companies and has provided an atmosphere for career development for more than 4,000 Rensselaer students in attendance each year. This year we expect to do no less.
